tes.<br></li><li>Save and load your own presets.<br></li><li>Export your animations into a spritesheet, .GIF or export it by single frames. 128x128 max.<br></li><li>Tool in continuous development, new features will be added over time.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046770/extras/5c1f3f61152f1969bb36733c33cc9f0e.poster.avif?t=1685351520\" width=426 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046770/extras/5c1f3f61152f1969bb36733c33cc9f0e.webm?t=1685351520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046770/extras/5c1f3f61152f1969bb36733c33cc9f0e.mp4?t=1685351520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
